products.name: Flanders Precisionaire 24 In. X 24 In. X 12 In. 85% Standard Rigid Synthetic Merv 14 Air Filter (case Of 1)
products.description:
MFG# PRP85S4412
Rigid Air extended surface area filters are designed for use in most commercial and industrial HVAC systems where medium and high efficiency filtration is required. These filters are especially suitable for variable air volume systems. These rigid filters are held into place by plastic pleat separators in a single header, box type frame.
MERV 14
Ecologically advanced filtration medium made entirely from recycled materials
Rugged corrosion-resistant steel casing minimizes damage during shipping and handling
Filters can operate with variable air speeds up to 625 FPM in temperatures up to 180 DEG F
